  "description": "Clean portfolio to showcase your creative work with project cards and an about section.",
  "category": "personal",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>My Portfolio</title>\n  <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"My Portfolio\">\n  <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Creative work and projects\">\n  <style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; background: #f8fafc; color: #1e293b; }\n    header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed); color: white; padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center; }\n    header h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 12px; }\n    header p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }\n    main { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 24px; }\n    .projects { display: grid; gap: 24px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); }\n    .card { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: transform 0.2s; }\n    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }\n    .card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #4f46e5; }\n    .card p { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; }\n    .tags { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }\n    .tags span { background: #eef2ff; color: #4f46e5; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 99px; font-size: 0.8rem; }\n    footer { text-align: center; padding: 32px; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h1>Your Name</h1>\n    <p>Designer & developer creating thoughtful digital experiences</p>\n  </header>\n  <main>\n    <section class=\"projects\">\n      <article class=\"card\">\n        <h3>Brand Redesign</h3>\n        <p>Complete visual identity refresh for a sustainable fashion startup, including logo, typography, and packaging.</p>\n        <div class=\"tags\"><span>Branding</span><span>Design</span></div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"card\">\n        <h3>Mobile App</h3>\n        <p>Fitness tracking app with social features, built with React Native and a custom animation library.</p>\n        <div class=\"tags\"><span>React Native</span><span>UI/UX</span></div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"card\">\n        <h3>E-commerce Platform</h3>\n        <p>Full-stack marketplace connecting local artisans with customers, handling payments and inventory.</p>\n        <div class=\"tags\"><span>Full Stack</span><span>E-commerce</span></div>\n      </article>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n  <footer>Built with Flowin</footer>\n</body>\n</html>"
}
